Pseudo Code
-----------

themes.php:
		start a session

		check if there is POST input

		if yes => save the theme name in the session and quit

			if theme name is "clear", clear the session

		start HTML, head, body (to enable Javascript)

		pass "theme" parameter to a Javascript variable

		render the rest of the HTML page with Javascript
		(each button hit sends a POST request 
		 with the session name to the same script)

